
  To switch to Windows containers:

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -SwitchWindowsEngine

  To switch to Linux containers:

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -SwitchLinuxEngine

  Other useful Docker CLI commands:

   1. List shared drives:

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -SharedDrives

   2. Shutdown Docker Desktop:

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -Shutdown

   3. Switch engine (toggle between Windows and Linux):

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -SwitchDaemon

   4. Enable verbose logging:

   1 & "C:\Program Files\Docker\Docker\DockerCli.exe" -Verbose
